<h1>Found a pet?</h1>

<%= link_to 'Check out our listings of missing pets',  posts_path, class: "block" %>

<p>What to do: <%= link_to " (More Info)", "http://www.americanhumane.org/animals/adoption-pet-care/caring-for-your-pet/if-you-find-a-lost-pet.html"%></p>
<ol>
  <li>1) Capture and contain it with care</li>
  <li>2) Call the authorities</li>
  <li>3) Check for ID</li>
  <li>4) Get the pet scanned for a microchip</li>
  <li>5) Take pets with no ID to an animal shelter</li>
  <li>6) Post fliers <%= link_to ' (Create flier here)', found_form_path%></li>
</ol>

